headline: Rep. Ryan hosts meet and greet Monday
author: BELLEFONTAINE EXAMINER STAFF
sentences: Rep. Tim Ryan, candidate for the U.S. Senate, hosts a meet and greet event at Red Apple Barn, 593 W. Township Road 199, Bellefontaine, from 5 to 6 p.m. Monday, Jan. 24.
